From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: experintellia <claude@example.com>
Date: Thu, 9 Jul 2026 16:17:40 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 23/37] web-app: use the SlothfulChat icon in the About dialog
 and welcome screen

Replaces the upstream Delta Chat intro1.png logo with our own app icon
(packages/web-app/static/images/icon-512.png, already bundled into
dist/images/ by assemble.mjs) in both the About dialog and the welcome
screen, with a slight border-radius so it reads as an app icon.

Also drops the About dialog's redundant "Delta Chat Browser Edition"
heading (the dialog title above it already says "About SlothfulChat"),
and clarifies in the body text that it's a fork of Delta Chat Desktop's
browser edition web UI, in addition to the chatmail core.

Moves the welcome screen's Source code/Imprint links out of the
onboarding form and into a DialogFooter, since inline they wrapped
awkwardly next to the buttons.
---
